Version 1.7.3

Apr-2026, Bug fixes
  - Fix Sensor cache round-trip losing the natural index
  - Fix PD0::Common::dump printing signed values as unsigned
  - Fix decompressTWR silently succeeding on errors and leaking temp files on
    rename failure
  - Fix Header::trim leaving all-whitespace strings untouched
  - Fix NetCDF destructor throwing during stack unwinding
  - Fix pd02netCDF lacking top-level exception handling
  - Fix dbd2csv second-pass skipping try/catch around Header/KnownBytes
    (dbd2netCDF already wrapped these)
  - Fix pd02netCDF hdr_* variables leaving gaps for record-less input files

Apr-2026, Build and CI
  - Move CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE default ahead of add_subdirectory(src)
  - Extract dbd_set_warnings() to remove duplicated warning flags
  - Move Data.C into dbd_common (was compiled 3x)
  - Remove non-functional CYGWIN CPack branch and its broken helpers
  - Remove unused HAVE_* config macros and dead CMake checks
  - Narrow cppcheck uninitMemberVar suppression to the one real site

Apr-2026, Tests
  - Add KnownBytes unit tests and decompressTWR integration test
  - Add --compression / --batch-size / --sensorOutput integration coverage
  - Consolidate fuzz corpus into test/fuzz/corpus/ with seeds for all 5 targets
  - Update benchmarks to Catch2 v3 link-based main

Apr-2026, Documentation
  - Add manpages for pd02netCDF and decompressTWR
  - Sync fuzz target inventory across CLAUDE.md, ARCHITECTURE.md, README,
    workflow
  - Fix column-major Data layout comment in ARCHITECTURE.md
  - Backfill 1.7.1 and 1.7.2 ChangeLog entries
  - Polish manpages (grammar, softened world-writeable warning, dropped
    --keepFirst)

Apr-2026, Hygiene
  - Remove inert --keepFirst flag and qKeepFirst variable
  - Remove undefined Sensors::mapSensors declaration and data.delim no-op
  - Rename NetCDF::putVars -> putVara to match the nc_put_vara_* call
  - INSTALL.sh exits 1 on unknown option and quotes cmake arguments
  - Header nLines initial guess 10 -> 14 to match documentation
  - std::nan("") consistency; lazy compression-label construction
  - stdint.h -> cstdint in KnownBytes.H and PD0.H

Version 1.7.2

Apr-2026, Build and CI
  - Apply -Wold-style-cast only to C++ files (lets lz4.c compile cleanly)
  - Add zlib to the Windows conda environment
  - Bump Catch2 to v3.14.0
  - Opt release and Windows jobs into Node.js 24

Apr-2026, New features
  - Add --skipAll and --sort flags to dbd2netCDF and dbd2csv

Apr-2026, Bug fixes
  - Harden binary parsing, logging, and NetCDF output paths

Version 1.7.1

